= The Pro-Patent Lobby trashes the directive =

----

This page tries to collect bits about the behaviour of the pro-patent lobby to trash the directive, especially in correlation with members of the EPP.

----

== List of bits ==

 * Jonas Maebe reported that BSA and EICTA had a meeting on monday, and decided afterwards to contact MEP Lehne to ask for rejection.
 * CompTIA was calling for rejection on wednesday already?
 * The big 5 (Siemens, Alcatel, Ericsson, Nokia, Philips) has called for rejection in the press
 * The PPE party was waiting for the decision of the PSE meeting
